item.title: CVE-2022-27893|2024-08-03T05:41:10.982Z -- palantir -- foundry%20magritte%20plugin%20osisoft-pi-web-connector
item.description: The Foundry Magritte plugin osisoft-pi-web-connector versions 0.15.0 - 0.43.0 was found to be logging in a manner that captured authentication requests. This vulnerability is resolved in osisoft-pi-web-connector version 0.44.0.
